{"ID":270355, "Text":"<div class=\"page\"><div class=\"pageNum\"><a name=\"355\"><\/a><div class=\"prev\"><a href=\"stpjs354.html\">Prev<\/a><\/div><div class=\"next\"><a href=\"stpjs356.html\">Next<\/a><\/div>\n\t\t\t    STPJS 355<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">This is good doctrine.<span class=\"footRef\">1<\/span> It tastes good.<span class=\"footRef\">2<\/span> I can taste the principles of eternal life,<span class=\"footRef\">3<\/span> and so can you.\n  They are given to me by the revelations of Jesus Christ;<span class=\"footRef\">4<\/span> and I know that when I tell you these words\n  of eternal life<span class=\"footRef\">5<\/span> as they are given to me, you taste them, and I know that you believe them. You say\n  honey is sweet,<span class=\"footRef\">6<\/span> and so do I. I can also taste the spirit of eternal life.<span class=\"footRef\">7<\/span> I know it is good;<span class=\"footRef\">8<\/span> and when\n  I tell you of these things which were given me by inspiration of the Holy Spirit,<span class=\"footRef\">9<\/span> you are bound to\n  receive them as sweet, and rejoice more and more.<span class=\"footRef\">10<\/span><\/p>\n  <div class=\"topic \">The Relation of Man to God<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">I want to talk more of the relation of man to God. I will open your eyes<span class=\"footRef\">11<\/span> in relation to your\n  dead. All things whatsoever God in his infinite wisdom<span class=\"footRef\">12<\/span> has seen fit<span class=\"footRef\">13<\/span> and proper to reveal to us,\n  while we are dwelling in mortality, in regard to our mortal bodies,<span class=\"footRef\">14<\/span> are revealed to us in the abstract,\n  and independent of affinity of this mortal tabernacle, but are revealed to our spirits precisely as\n  though we had no bodies at all; and those revelations which will save our spirits will save our\n  bodies.<span class=\"footRef\">15<\/span> God reveals them to us in view of no eternal dissolution of the body, or tabernacle. Hence\n  the responsibility, the awful responsibility, that rests upon us in relation to our dead;<span class=\"footRef\">16<\/span> for all the\n  spirits who have not obeyed the Gospel in the flesh must either obey it in the spirit<span class=\"footRef\">17<\/span> or be damned.\n  Solemn thought!&mdash;dreadful thought! Is there nothing to be done?&mdash;no preparation&mdash;no salvation\n  for our fathers and friends who have died without having had the opportunity to obey the decrees\n  of the Son of Man? Would to God that I had forty days and nights<span class=\"footRef\">18<\/span> in which to tell you all! I would\n  let you know that I am not a &ldquo;fallen prophet.&rdquo;<span class=\"footRef\">19<\/span><span class=\"textFootRef\">,a<\/span><\/p>\n  <div class=\"footnotes\">\n    <div class=\"footnote\">1. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106921\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106921)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106921)\">Prov. 4:2<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110016\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110016)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110016)\">1 Tim. 4:6<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">2. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106865\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106865)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106865)\">Ps. 119:103<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106692\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106692)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106692)\">Ps. 34:8<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110190\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110190)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110190)\">Heb. 6:5<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116835\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116835)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116835)\">Moses 6:55<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">3. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116146\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116146)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116146)\">D&amp;C 128:12<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">4. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109718\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109718)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109718)\">Gal. 1:12<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">5. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108704\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108704)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108704)\">John 6:68<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114697\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114697)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114697)\">D&amp;C 84:43<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115130\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115130)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115130)\">D&amp;C 98:20<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116843\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116843)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116843)\">Moses 6:59<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">6. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106945\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106945)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106945)\">Prov. 16:24<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106958\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106958)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106958)\">Prov. 24:13<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">7. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112121\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112121)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112121)\">Alma 32:42<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112191\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112191)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112191)\">Alma 36:24<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">8. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116763\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116763)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116763)\">Moses 4:11-12<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">9. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110073\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110073)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110073)\">2 Tim. 3:16<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113339\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113339)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113339)\">D&amp;C 20:10<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116804\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116804)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116804)\">Moses 6:5<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">10. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109952\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109952)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109952)\">1 Thes. 5:16<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115112\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115112)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115112)\">D&amp;C 98:1<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">11. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114392\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114392)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114392)\">D&amp;C 76:12<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">12. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106903\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106903)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106903)\">Ps. 147:5<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">13. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111735\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111735)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111735)\">Mosiah 27:28<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">14. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109290\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109290)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109290)\">Rom. 8:11<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111895\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111895)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111895)\">Alma 11:45<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112788\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112788)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112788)\">Morm. 6:21<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">15. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113540\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113540)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113540)\">D&amp;C 29:34-35<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">16. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116158\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116158)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116158)\">D&amp;C 128:15<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">17. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116662\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116662)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116662)\">D&amp;C 138:30-37<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">18. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106185\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106185)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106185)\">Ex. 24:18<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107799\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107799)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107799)\">Matt. 4:2<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108896\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108896)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108896)\">Acts 1:3<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">19. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109084\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109084)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109084)\">Acts 13:6<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111630\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111630)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111630)\">Mosiah 15:13<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112501\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112501)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112501)\">Hel. 13:26<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n  <div class=\"textFootnotes\">\n    \n      <p class=\"cont\">brings into eternal union &ldquo;spirit and element&rdquo; declared by the word of God to be essential to a fulness of joy&mdash;&ldquo;The elements are eternal, and spirit and element, inseparably connected, receive a fulness of joy;\n        and when separated man cannot receive a fulness of joy&rdquo; (Doc. and Cov., Sec. 93). Also, &ldquo;Adam fell that men might be: and men are that they might have joy&rdquo; (2 Nephi 2:25). Indeed, the whole purpose of God in bringing to pass the earth life of man is to inure to the welfare and enlargement of man as urged in the teaching of the Prophet in the paragraph above. God affects man only to his advantage. See also Seventy&rsquo;s Year Book No. 2, Lesson ii, note 6.&mdash; Note by Elder B. H. Roberts.<\/p>\n    \n    \n      <p class=\"std\"><span class=\"textMark\">a<\/span>Accusations were repeatedly being made about this time that President Smith was a fallen prophet. But when the mighty doctrines that in this discourse he is setting forth are taken into account, and the spiritual power with which he is delivering them is reckoned with, no more complete refuta-<\/p>\n    \n  <\/div>\n<\/div>"}